OL,3,CSEND mum slams Worcestershire
OL,4,Ccouncillors as Green Tory coalition is
OL,5,Cin crisis
OL,7,FYesterday, 14th May, the
OL,8,FConservatives, Lib Dems, Greens and
OL,9,FIndependents joined forces to wrestle
OL,10,Fpower away from Reform UK.
OL,12,FThe coalition successfully installed
OL,13,FGreen councillor Matt Jenkins as
OL,14,Fleader, but had the rug pulled out
OL,15,Ffrom under them when the Conservative
OL,16,Fdeputy leader was suspended from the
OL,17,FTory party by the Conservative head
OL,18,Foffice in Westminster.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1779034270
OL,3,CSEND mum slams Worcestershire
OL,4,Ccouncillors as Green Tory coalition is
OL,5,Cin crisis
OL,7,FWhilst Cllr Jenkins has told ITV News
OL,8,FCentral he has options to make this
OL,9,Fadministration work, some in the
OL,10,Fcounty say that this uncertainty is
OL,11,Fbad for residents.
OL,13,FMs Styles' daughter is in her 20s and
OL,14,Fhas special educational needs. She
OL,15,Fstruggles to read and write
OL,16,Findependently.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
