CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1779034270
OL,3,CSEND mum slams Worcestershire
OL,4,Ccouncillors as Green Tory coalition is
OL,5,Cin crisis
OL,7,F"Worcestershire Council has been in
OL,8,Fchaos since Reform took over.
OL,10,F"They have hiked council tax by nine
OL,11,Fpercent and Nigel Farage now says he
OL,12,Fwish Reform had never bothered trying
OL,13,Fto run it."
OL,15,FLeader Matt Jenkins has said: "Tory HQ
OL,16,Fshould keep out of it ` this is a
OL,17,Flocal matter, we're just trying to do
OL,18,Fthe best for local residents."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUuD@KO]wD@_OUzD@^O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
