OL,3,CSEND mum slams Worcestershire
OL,4,Ccouncillors as Green Tory coalition is
OL,5,Cin crisis
OL,7,FIndependent councillor, and former
OL,8,FReform deputy leader, David Taylor
OL,9,Fsaid: "Worcestershire needs
OL,10,Fcooperation, not conflict.
OL,12,F"It needs local decisionmaking,
OL,13,Fcrossparty working and a focus on
OL,14,Fpractical outcomes, not party
OL,15,Fdiscipline from afar.
OL,17,F"Residents deserve solutions, not
OL,18,Fpolitical pointscoring.
OL,26,@qD@GOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
